		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="407" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">What else? I must confess I'm a bit of a shopaholic! The shops here are fabulous - although some of them are on the expensive side. There are lots of [19] to be had though, especially in the [20]. I'll show you where they all are when you get here!</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
